      "title": "Chicken",
      "pageid": 1890,
      "text": "<div class=\"mw-parser-output\"><div id=\"infoboxborder\">\n<table id=\"infoboxtable\">\n<tbody><tr>\n<td colspan=\"2\" id=\"infoboxheader\">Chicken\n</td></tr>\n<tr>\n<td colspan=\"2\" style=\"text-align: center; padding-bottom: 5px;\"><img alt=\"White Chicken.png\" src=\"/mediawiki/images/2/22/White_Chicken.png\" decoding=\"async\" width=\"48\" height=\"48\" />&#160;<img alt=\"Brown Chicken.png\" src=\"/mediawiki/images/f/fd/Brown_Chicken.png\" decoding=\"async\" width=\"48\" height=\"48\" />&#160;<img alt=\"Blue Chicken.png\" src=\"/mediawiki/images/6/61/Blue_Chicken.png\" decoding=\"async\" width=\"48\" height=\"48\" />\n</td></tr>\n<tr>\n<td colspan=\"2\" id=\"infoboxdetail\" style=\"text-align: center; font-style: italic;\">Well cared-for adult chickens lay eggs every day.  Lives in the coop.\n</td></tr>\n<tr>\n<td colspan=\"2\" id=\"infoboxsection\" style=\"text-align: center;\">Information\n</td></tr>\n<tr>\n<td id=\"infoboxsection\">Building\n</td>\n<td id=\"infoboxdetail\"><style data-mw-deduplicate=\"TemplateStyles:r120955\">.mw-parser-output .nametemplate{margin:2px 5px 1px 2px;display:block;white-space:nowrap}.mw-parser-output .nametemplateinline{margin:2px 0 1px 2px;display:inline;white-space:nowrap}.mw-parser-output .nametemplate img,.mw-parser-output .nametemplateinline img{max-width:none}</style><span class=\"nametemplate\"><img alt=\"Coop.png\" src=\"/mediawiki/images/thumb/4/48/Coop.png/24px-Coop.png\" decoding=\"async\" width=\"24\" height=\"27\" srcset=\"/mediawiki/images/thumb/4/48/Coop.png/36px-Coop.png 1.5x, /mediawiki/images/thumb/4/48/Coop.png/48px-Coop.png 2x\" /> <a href=\"/Coop\" title=\"Coop\">Coop</a></span>\n</td></tr>\n<tr>\n<td id=\"infoboxsection\">Purchase Price\n</td>\n<td id=\"infoboxdetail\"><span style=\"display: none;\">data-sort-value=\"800 \"&gt;</span><span class=\"no-wrap\"><img alt=\"Gold.png\" src=\"/mediawiki/images/thumb/1/10/Gold.png/18px-Gold.png\" decoding=\"async\" width=\"18\" height=\"18\" srcset=\"/mediawiki/images/thumb/1/10/Gold.png/27px-Gold.png 1.5x, /mediawiki/images/thumb/1/10/Gold.png/36px-Gold.png 2x\" />800g</span>\n</td></tr>\n<tr>\n<td id=\"infoboxsection\">Produce\n</td>\n<td id=\"infoboxdetail\"><link rel=\"mw-deduplicated-inline-style\" href=\"mw-data:TemplateStyles:r120955\"/><span class=\"nametemplate\"><img alt=\"Egg.png\" src=\"/mediawiki/images/thumb/2/26/Egg.png/24px-Egg.png\" decoding=\"async\" width=\"24\" height=\"24\" srcset=\"/mediawiki/images/thumb/2/26/Egg.png/36px-Egg.png 1.5x, /mediawiki/images/2/26/Egg.png 2x\" /> <a href=\"/Egg\" title=\"Egg\">Egg</a></span><link rel=\"mw-deduplicated-inline-style\" href=\"mw-data:TemplateStyles:r120955\"/><span class=\"nametemplate\"><img alt=\"Brown Egg.png\" src=\"/mediawiki/images/thumb/0/01/Brown_Egg.png/24px-Brown_Egg.png\" decoding=\"async\" width=\"24\" height=\"24\" srcset=\"/mediawiki/images/thumb/0/01/Brown_Egg.png/36px-Brown_Egg.png 1.5x, /mediawiki/images/0/01/Brown_Egg.png 2x\" /> <a href=\"/Egg\" title=\"Egg\">Brown Egg</a></span><link rel=\"mw-deduplicated-inline-style\" href=\"mw-data:TemplateStyles:r120955\"/><span class=\"nametemplate\"><img alt=\"Large Egg.png\" src=\"/mediawiki/images/thumb/5/5d/Large_Egg.png/24px-Large_Egg.png\" decoding=\"async\" width=\"24\" height=\"24\" srcset=\"/mediawiki/images/thumb/5/5d/Large_Egg.png/36px-Large_Egg.png 1.5x, /mediawiki/images/5/5d/Large_Egg.png 2x\" /> <a href=\"/Large_Egg\" title=\"Large Egg\">Large Egg</a></span><link rel=\"mw-deduplicated-inline-style\" href=\"mw-data:TemplateStyles:r120955\"/><span class=\"nametemplate\"><img alt=\"Large Brown Egg.png\" src=\"/mediawiki/images/thumb/9/91/Large_Brown_Egg.png/24px-Large_Brown_Egg.png\" decoding=\"async\" width=\"24\" height=\"24\" srcset=\"/mediawiki/images/thumb/9/91/Large_Brown_Egg.png/36px-Large_Brown_Egg.png 1.5x, /mediawiki/images/9/91/Large_Brown_Egg.png 2x\" /> <a href=\"/Large_Egg\" title=\"Large Egg\">Large Brown Egg</a></span>\n</td></tr>\n</tbody></table></div>\n<dl><dd><i>See also: <a href=\"/Golden_Chicken\" title=\"Golden Chicken\">Golden Chicken</a>, <a href=\"/Void_Chicken\" title=\"Void Chicken\">Void Chicken</a></i></dd></dl>\n<p>The <b>Chicken</b> is a farm <a href=\"/Animals\" title=\"Animals\">animal</a> that lives in a <a href=\"/Coop\" title=\"Coop\">Coop</a>. Chickens can be purchased at <a href=\"/Marnie%27s_Ranch\" title=\"Marnie&#39;s Ranch\">Marnie's Ranch</a> for <span style=\"display: none;\">data-sort-value=\"800\"&gt;</span><span class=\"no-wrap\"><img alt=\"Gold.png\" src=\"/mediawiki/images/thumb/1/10/Gold.png/18px-Gold.png\" decoding=\"async\" width=\"18\" height=\"18\" srcset=\"/mediawiki/images/thumb/1/10/Gold.png/27px-Gold.png 1.5x, /mediawiki/images/thumb/1/10/Gold.png/36px-Gold.png 2x\" />800g</span> or hatched by placing an <a href=\"/Egg\" title=\"Egg\">Egg</a> into an <a href=\"/Incubator\" title=\"Incubator\">Incubator</a>, taking <style data-mw-deduplicate=\"TemplateStyles:r120974\">.mw-parser-output .durationtemplate{margin:2px 5px 1px 2px;display:block;white-space:nowrap}.mw-parser-output .durationtemplateinline{margin:2px 0 1px 2px;display:inline;white-space:nowrap}.mw-parser-output .durationtemplate img,.mw-parser-output .durationtemplateinline img{max-width:none}</style><span class=\"durationtemplateinline\"><img alt=\"Time Icon.png\" src=\"/mediawiki/images/thumb/7/70/Time_Icon.png/24px-Time_Icon.png\" decoding=\"async\" width=\"24\" height=\"24\" srcset=\"/mediawiki/images/thumb/7/70/Time_Icon.png/36px-Time_Icon.png 1.5x, /mediawiki/images/7/70/Time_Icon.png 2x\" /> 9,000m (5d 16h 40m)</span> to incubate, or <link rel=\"mw-deduplicated-inline-style\" href=\"mw-data:TemplateStyles:r120974\"/><span class=\"durationtemplateinline\"><img alt=\"Time Icon.png\" src=\"/mediawiki/images/thumb/7/70/Time_Icon.png/24px-Time_Icon.png\" decoding=\"async\" width=\"24\" height=\"24\" srcset=\"/mediawiki/images/thumb/7/70/Time_Icon.png/36px-Time_Icon.png 1.5x, /mediawiki/images/7/70/Time_Icon.png 2x\" /> 4,500m (2d 21h 40m)</span> with the <a href=\"/Farming#Farming_Skill\" title=\"Farming\">Coopmaster Profession</a>. Additionally, two chickens are present on the farm by default on the Meadowlands <a href=\"/Farm_Maps\" title=\"Farm Maps\">Farm Map</a>.\n</p>\n<div id=\"toc\" class=\"toc\" role=\"navigation\" aria-labelledby=\"mw-toc-heading\"><input type=\"checkbox\" role=\"button\" id=\"toctogglecheckbox\" class=\"toctogglecheckbox\" style=\"display:none\" /><div class=\"toctitle\" lang=\"en\" dir=\"ltr\"><h2 id=\"mw-toc-heading\">Contents</h2><span class=\"toctogglespan\"><label class=\"toctogglelabel\" for=\"toctogglecheckbox\"></label></span></div>\n<ul>\n<li class=\"toclevel-1 tocsection-1\"><a href=\"#Color\"><span class=\"tocnumber\">1</span> <span class=\"toctext\">Color</span></a></li>\n<li class=\"toclevel-1 tocsection-2\"><a href=\"#Produce\"><span class=\"tocnumber\">2</span> <span class=\"toctext\">Produce</span></a></li>\n<li class=\"toclevel-1 tocsection-3\"><a href=\"#Blue_Chickens\"><span class=\"tocnumber\">3</span> <span class=\"toctext\">Blue Chickens</span></a></li>\n<li class=\"toclevel-1 tocsection-4\"><a href=\"#Selling\"><span class=\"tocnumber\">4</span> <span class=\"toctext\">Selling</span></a></li>\n<li class=\"toclevel-1 tocsection-5\"><a href=\"#Trivia\"><span class=\"tocnumber\">5</span> <span class=\"toctext\">Trivia</span></a></li>\n<li class=\"toclevel-1 tocsection-6\"><a href=\"#References\"><span class=\"tocnumber\">6</span> <span class=\"toctext\">References</span></a></li>\n<li class=\"toclevel-1 tocsection-7\"><a href=\"#History\"><span class=\"tocnumber\">7</span> <span class=\"toctext\">History</span></a></li>\n</ul>\n</div>\n\n<h2><span class=\"mw-headline\" id=\"Color\">Color</span><span class=\"mw-editsection\"><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">[</span><a href=\"/mediawiki/index.php?title=Chicken&amp;action=edit&amp;section=1\" title=\"Edit section: Color\">edit</a><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">]</span></span></h2>\n<p>Chickens are colored White, Brown, or Blue. The Blue variety can be obtained only after seeing <a href=\"/Shane\" title=\"Shane\">Shane</a>'s 8-heart event. The color of the chicken is assigned randomly by the game when a chicken is purchased.\n</p><p>While selecting a coop for a Chicken purchased from Marnie's Ranch, a message is shown stating \"Choose a Coop for your new White/Brown/Blue Chicken\". Cancelling the purchase returns the player to the purchase window, where they can try again for the desired color.\n</p><p>An <a href=\"/Incubator\" title=\"Incubator\">Incubator</a> will hatch a brown chicken from a <a href=\"/Egg\" title=\"Egg\">Brown Egg</a> and a white chicken from a regular Egg (or the corresponding Large variants). This means blue chickens cannot be obtained using an Incubator.<sup id=\"cite_ref-1\" class=\"reference\"><a href=\"#cite_note-1\">&#91;1&#93;</a></sup>\n</p><p>White and blue chickens produce white eggs, and brown chickens produce brown eggs, so it makes a difference in completing the <a href=\"/Community_Center\" title=\"Community Center\">Community Center</a> <a href=\"/Bundles\" title=\"Bundles\">Bundles</a>, especially if <a href=\"/Options#Advanced_Options\" title=\"Options\">Remixed Bundles</a> is not chosen at start of game.\n</p>\n<h2><span class=\"mw-headline\" id=\"Produce\">Produce</span><span class=\"mw-editsection\"><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">[</span><a href=\"/mediawiki/index.php?title=Chicken&amp;action=edit&amp;section=2\" title=\"Edit section: Produce\">edit</a><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">]</span></span></h2>\n<dl><dd><i>Main article: <a href=\"/Animals#Produce\" title=\"Animals\">Animals#Produce</a></i></dd></dl>\n<p>Chickens who eat every day mature after 3 nights have passed. A mature and fed chicken produces a white or brown <a href=\"/Egg\" title=\"Egg\">Egg</a> every day, which can be placed in an <a href=\"/Incubator\" title=\"Incubator\">Incubator</a> to hatch another chicken, or sold for <span style=\"display: none;\">data-sort-value=\"50\"&gt;</span><span class=\"no-wrap\"><img alt=\"Gold.png\" src=\"/mediawiki/images/thumb/1/10/Gold.png/18px-Gold.png\" decoding=\"async\" width=\"18\" height=\"18\" srcset=\"/mediawiki/images/thumb/1/10/Gold.png/27px-Gold.png 1.5x, /mediawiki/images/thumb/1/10/Gold.png/36px-Gold.png 2x\" />50g</span>. Once sufficient <a href=\"/Animals#Friendship\" title=\"Animals\">friendship</a> and happiness is reached, it has a chance to produce a <a href=\"/Large_Egg\" title=\"Large Egg\">Large Egg</a> or <a href=\"/Large_Egg\" title=\"Large Egg\">Large Brown Egg</a> which sells for <span style=\"display: none;\">data-sort-value=\"95\"&gt;</span><span class=\"no-wrap\"><img alt=\"Gold.png\" src=\"/mediawiki/images/thumb/1/10/Gold.png/18px-Gold.png\" decoding=\"async\" width=\"18\" height=\"18\" srcset=\"/mediawiki/images/thumb/1/10/Gold.png/27px-Gold.png 1.5x, /mediawiki/images/thumb/1/10/Gold.png/36px-Gold.png 2x\" />95g</span>.\n</p><p>An Egg can be placed in the <a href=\"/Mayonnaise_Machine\" title=\"Mayonnaise Machine\">Mayonnaise Machine</a> to produce <a href=\"/Mayonnaise\" title=\"Mayonnaise\">Mayonnaise</a>, which sells for <span style=\"display: none;\">data-sort-value=\"190\"&gt;</span><span class=\"no-wrap\"><img alt=\"Gold.png\" src=\"/mediawiki/images/thumb/1/10/Gold.png/18px-Gold.png\" decoding=\"async\" width=\"18\" height=\"18\" srcset=\"/mediawiki/images/thumb/1/10/Gold.png/27px-Gold.png 1.5x, /mediawiki/images/thumb/1/10/Gold.png/36px-Gold.png 2x\" />190g</span> or <span style=\"display: none;\">data-sort-value=\"285\"&gt;</span><span class=\"no-wrap\"><img alt=\"Gold.png\" src=\"/mediawiki/images/thumb/1/10/Gold.png/18px-Gold.png\" decoding=\"async\" width=\"18\" height=\"18\" srcset=\"/mediawiki/images/thumb/1/10/Gold.png/27px-Gold.png 1.5x, /mediawiki/images/thumb/1/10/Gold.png/36px-Gold.png 2x\" />285g</span> depending on quality.\n</p>\n<table class=\"wikitable roundedborder\">\n<tbody><tr>\n<th>Image\n</th>\n<th>Name\n</th>\n<th>Description\n</th>\n<th>Sell Price\n</th></tr>\n<tr>\n<td><a href=\"/File:Egg.png\" class=\"image\"><img alt=\"Egg.png\" src=\"/mediawiki/images/2/26/Egg.png\" decoding=\"async\" width=\"48\" height=\"48\" /></a> <a href=\"/File:Brown_Egg.png\" class=\"image\"><img alt=\"Brown Egg.png\" src=\"/mediawiki/images/0/01/Brown_Egg.png\" decoding=\"async\" width=\"48\" height=\"48\" /></a>\n</td>\n<td><a href=\"/Egg\" title=\"Egg\">Egg</a><br /><a href=\"/Egg\" title=\"Egg\">Brown Egg</a>\n</td>\n<td>A regular white chicken egg.<br />A regular brown chicken egg.\n</td>\n<td><table class=\"no-wrap\" style=\"text-align: left; margin: 0; padding: 0; border-spacing: 0; border: 0;\">\n<tbody><tr>\n\t<td><style data-mw-deduplicate=\"TemplateStyles:r146727\">.mw-parser-output .parent,.mw-parser-output .backimage,.mw-parser-output .backimagetransparent{position:relative;top:0;left:0}.mw-parser-output .backimage img,.mw-parser-output .foreimage img,.mw-parser-output .backimagetransparent img{display:block}.mw-parser-output .backimagetransparent img{opacity:0.6}.mw-parser-output .foreimage{position:absolute;bottom:0;right:0}</style><div class=\"parent\" style=\"width: 24px; height: auto; margin: 0 auto;\"><div class=\"backimage\"><img alt=\"Egg.png\" src=\"/mediawiki/images/thumb/2/26/Egg.png/24px-Egg.png\" decoding=\"async\" width=\"24\" height=\"24\" srcset=\"/mediawiki/images/thumb/2/26/Egg.png/36px-Egg.png 1.5x, /mediawiki/images/2/26/Egg.png 2x\" /></div><div class=\"foreimage\"></div></div></td>\n\t<td>50g\n\t</td>\n</tr><tr>\n\t<td><link rel=\"mw-deduplicated-inline-style\" href=\"mw-data:TemplateStyles:r146727\"/><div class=\"parent\" style=\"width: 24px; height: auto; margin: 0 auto;\"><div class=\"backimage\"><img alt=\"Egg.png\" src=\"/mediawiki/images/thumb/2/26/Egg.png/24px-Egg.png\" decoding=\"async\" width=\"24\" height=\"24\" srcset=\"/mediawiki/images/thumb/2/26/Egg.png/36px-Egg.png 1.5x, /mediawiki/images/2/26/Egg.png 2x\" /></div><div class=\"foreimage\"><img alt=\"Silver Quality Icon.png\" src=\"/mediawiki/images/thumb/8/8a/Silver_Quality_Icon.png/24px-Silver_Quality_Icon.png\" decoding=\"async\" width=\"24\" height=\"24\" srcset=\"/mediawiki/images/thumb/8/8a/Silver_Quality_Icon.png/36px-Silver_Quality_Icon.png 1.5x, /mediawiki/images/8/8a/Silver_Quality_Icon.png 2x\" /></div></div></td>\n\t<td>62g\n\t</td>\n</tr><tr>\n\t<td><link rel=\"mw-deduplicated-inline-style\" href=\"mw-data:TemplateStyles:r146727\"/><div class=\"parent\" style=\"width: 24px; height: auto; margin: 0 auto;\"><div class=\"backimage\"><img alt=\"Egg.png\" src=\"/mediawiki/images/thumb/2/26/Egg.png/24px-Egg.png\" decoding=\"async\" width=\"24\" height=\"24\" srcset=\"/mediawiki/images/thumb/2/26/Egg.png/36px-Egg.png 1.5x, /mediawiki/images/2/26/Egg.png 2x\" /></div><div class=\"foreimage\"><img alt=\"Gold Quality Icon.png\" src=\"/mediawiki/images/thumb/4/47/Gold_Quality_Icon.png/24px-Gold_Quality_Icon.png\" decoding=\"async\" width=\"24\" height=\"24\" srcset=\"/mediawiki/images/thumb/4/47/Gold_Quality_Icon.png/36px-Gold_Quality_Icon.png 1.5x, /mediawiki/images/4/47/Gold_Quality_Icon.png 2x\" /></div></div></td>\n\t<td>75g\n\t</td>\n</tr><tr>\n\t<td><link rel=\"mw-deduplicated-inline-style\" href=\"mw-data:TemplateStyles:r146727\"/><div class=\"parent\" style=\"width: 24px; height: auto; margin: 0 auto;\"><div class=\"backimage\"><img alt=\"Egg.png\" src=\"/mediawiki/images/thumb/2/26/Egg.png/24px-Egg.png\" decoding=\"async\" width=\"24\" height=\"24\" srcset=\"/mediawiki/images/thumb/2/26/Egg.png/36px-Egg.png 1.5x, /mediawiki/images/2/26/Egg.png 2x\" /></div><div class=\"foreimage\"><img alt=\"Iridium Quality Icon.png\" src=\"/mediawiki/images/thumb/e/e4/Iridium_Quality_Icon.png/24px-Iridium_Quality_Icon.png\" decoding=\"async\" width=\"24\" height=\"24\" srcset=\"/mediawiki/images/thumb/e/e4/Iridium_Quality_Icon.png/36px-Iridium_Quality_Icon.png 1.5x, /mediawiki/images/e/e4/Iridium_Quality_Icon.png 2x\" /></div></div></td>\n\t<td>100g\n\t</td>\n</tr></tbody></table>\n</td></tr>\n<tr>\n<td><a href=\"/File:Large_Egg.png\" class=\"image\"><img alt=\"Large Egg.png\" src=\"/mediawiki/images/5/5d/Large_Egg.png\" decoding=\"async\" width=\"48\" height=\"48\" /></a> <a href=\"/File:Large_Brown_Egg.png\" class=\"image\"><img alt=\"Large Brown Egg.png\" src=\"/mediawiki/images/9/91/Large_Brown_Egg.png\" decoding=\"async\" width=\"48\" height=\"48\" /></a>\n</td>\n<td><a href=\"/Large_Egg\" title=\"Large Egg\">Large Egg</a><br /><a href=\"/Large_Egg\" title=\"Large Egg\">Large Brown Egg</a>\n</td>\n<td>It's an uncommonly large white egg!<br />It's an uncommonly large brown egg!\n</td>\n<td><table class=\"no-wrap\" style=\"text-align: left; margin: 0; padding: 0; border-spacing: 0; border: 0;\">\n<tbody><tr>\n\t<td><link rel=\"mw-deduplicated-inline-style\" href=\"mw-data:TemplateStyles:r146727\"/><div class=\"parent\" style=\"width: 24px; height: auto; margin: 0 auto;\"><div class=\"backimage\"><img alt=\"Large Egg.png\" src=\"/mediawiki/images/thumb/5/5d/Large_Egg.png/24px-Large_Egg.png\" decoding=\"async\" width=\"24\" height=\"24\" srcset=\"/mediawiki/images/thumb/5/5d/Large_Egg.png/36px-Large_Egg.png 1.5x, /mediawiki/images/5/5d/Large_Egg.png 2x\" /></div><div class=\"foreimage\"></div></div></td>\n\t<td>95g\n\t</td>\n</tr><tr>\n\t<td><link rel=\"mw-deduplicated-inline-style\" href=\"mw-data:TemplateStyles:r146727\"/><div class=\"parent\" style=\"width: 24px; height: auto; margin: 0 auto;\"><div class=\"backimage\"><img alt=\"Large Egg.png\" src=\"/mediawiki/images/thumb/5/5d/Large_Egg.png/24px-Large_Egg.png\" decoding=\"async\" width=\"24\" height=\"24\" srcset=\"/mediawiki/images/thumb/5/5d/Large_Egg.png/36px-Large_Egg.png 1.5x, /mediawiki/images/5/5d/Large_Egg.png 2x\" /></div><div class=\"foreimage\"><img alt=\"Silver Quality Icon.png\" src=\"/mediawiki/images/thumb/8/8a/Silver_Quality_Icon.png/24px-Silver_Quality_Icon.png\" decoding=\"async\" width=\"24\" height=\"24\" srcset=\"/mediawiki/images/thumb/8/8a/Silver_Quality_Icon.png/36px-Silver_Quality_Icon.png 1.5x, /mediawiki/images/8/8a/Silver_Quality_Icon.png 2x\" /></div></div></td>\n\t<td>118g\n\t</td>\n</tr><tr>\n\t<td><link rel=\"mw-deduplicated-inline-style\" href=\"mw-data:TemplateStyles:r146727\"/><div class=\"parent\" style=\"width: 24px; height: auto; margin: 0 auto;\"><div class=\"backimage\"><img alt=\"Large Egg.png\" src=\"/mediawiki/images/thumb/5/5d/Large_Egg.png/24px-Large_Egg.png\" decoding=\"async\" width=\"24\" height=\"24\" srcset=\"/mediawiki/images/thumb/5/5d/Large_Egg.png/36px-Large_Egg.png 1.5x, /mediawiki/images/5/5d/Large_Egg.png 2x\" /></div><div class=\"foreimage\"><img alt=\"Gold Quality Icon.png\" src=\"/mediawiki/images/thumb/4/47/Gold_Quality_Icon.png/24px-Gold_Quality_Icon.png\" decoding=\"async\" width=\"24\" height=\"24\" srcset=\"/mediawiki/images/thumb/4/47/Gold_Quality_Icon.png/36px-Gold_Quality_Icon.png 1.5x, /mediawiki/images/4/47/Gold_Quality_Icon.png 2x\" /></div></div></td>\n\t<td>142g\n\t</td>\n</tr><tr>\n\t<td><link rel=\"mw-deduplicated-inline-style\" href=\"mw-data:TemplateStyles:r146727\"/><div class=\"parent\" style=\"width: 24px; height: auto; margin: 0 auto;\"><div class=\"backimage\"><img alt=\"Large Egg.png\" src=\"/mediawiki/images/thumb/5/5d/Large_Egg.png/24px-Large_Egg.png\" decoding=\"async\" width=\"24\" height=\"24\" srcset=\"/mediawiki/images/thumb/5/5d/Large_Egg.png/36px-Large_Egg.png 1.5x, /mediawiki/images/5/5d/Large_Egg.png 2x\" /></div><div class=\"foreimage\"><img alt=\"Iridium Quality Icon.png\" src=\"/mediawiki/images/thumb/e/e4/Iridium_Quality_Icon.png/24px-Iridium_Quality_Icon.png\" decoding=\"async\" width=\"24\" height=\"24\" srcset=\"/mediawiki/images/thumb/e/e4/Iridium_Quality_Icon.png/36px-Iridium_Quality_Icon.png 1.5x, /mediawiki/images/e/e4/Iridium_Quality_Icon.png 2x\" /></div></div></td>\n\t<td>190g\n\t</td>\n</tr></tbody></table>\n</td></tr></tbody></table>\n<h2><span class=\"mw-headline\" id=\"Blue_Chickens\">Blue Chickens</span><span class=\"mw-editsection\"><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">[</span><a href=\"/mediawiki/index.php?title=Chicken&amp;action=edit&amp;section=3\" title=\"Edit section: Blue Chickens\">edit</a><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">]</span></span></h2>\n<div class=\"thumb tright\"><div class=\"thumbinner\" style=\"width:77px;\"><a href=\"/File:BlueChick.png\" class=\"image\"><img alt=\"\" src=\"/mediawiki/images/thumb/3/36/BlueChick.png/75px-BlueChick.png\" decoding=\"async\" width=\"75\" height=\"75\" class=\"thumbimage\" srcset=\"/mediawiki/images/thumb/3/36/BlueChick.png/113px-BlueChick.png 1.5x, /mediawiki/images/thumb/3/36/BlueChick.png/150px-BlueChick.png 2x\" /></a>  <div class=\"thumbcaption\"><div class=\"magnify\"><a href=\"/File:BlueChick.png\" class=\"internal\" title=\"Enlarge\"></a></div>A blue chick</div></div></div><p>After seeing <a href=\"/Shane\" title=\"Shane\">Shane</a>'s 8-heart event, each chicken you purchase from <a href=\"/Marnie\" title=\"Marnie\">Marnie</a> has a 25% chance of being blue. Aside from appearance, blue chickens are identical to regular white and brown chickens. One subtle benefit to this alternative color is that blue chickens are much easier to spot in a field of grass.\n</p><p>Blue chickens are hatched as blue chicks.\n</p>\n<h2><span class=\"mw-headline\" id=\"Selling\">Selling</span><span class=\"mw-editsection\"><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">[</span><a href=\"/mediawiki/index.php?title=Chicken&amp;action=edit&amp;section=4\" title=\"Edit section: Selling\">edit</a><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">]</span></span></h2>\n<p>It is possible to sell Chickens. The amount of <a href=\"/Gold\" title=\"Gold\">gold</a> obtained for doing so is dependent on how many hearts the animal has. The more hearts; the higher amount of gold fetched for selling it. The amount of gold obtained for selling a maximum-heart Chicken is <span style=\"display: none;\">data-sort-value=\"1040\"&gt;</span><span class=\"no-wrap\"><img alt=\"Gold.png\" src=\"/mediawiki/images/thumb/1/10/Gold.png/18px-Gold.png\" decoding=\"async\" width=\"18\" height=\"18\" srcset=\"/mediawiki/images/thumb/1/10/Gold.png/27px-Gold.png 1.5x, /mediawiki/images/thumb/1/10/Gold.png/36px-Gold.png 2x\" />1,040g</span>.\n</p><p>To sell a coop or barn animal, right-click the animal after petting. The friendship/mood interface appears. Move the cursor over the gold coin button at the right to see how much you can sell the animal for. Click that button and the confirmation that follows to complete the sale.\n</p>\n<h2><span class=\"mw-headline\" id=\"Trivia\">Trivia</span><span class=\"mw-editsection\"><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">[</span><a href=\"/mediawiki/index.php?title=Chicken&amp;action=edit&amp;section=5\" title=\"Edit section: Trivia\">edit</a><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">]</span></span></h2>\n<ul><li>A blue chicken egg was added to the game <a href=\"https://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Terraria\" class=\"extiw\" title=\"wikipedia:Terraria\">Terraria</a> with ConcernedApe's permission in October 2022.</li></ul>\n<h2><span class=\"mw-headline\" id=\"References\">References</span><span class=\"mw-editsection\"><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">[</span><a href=\"/mediawiki/index.php?title=Chicken&amp;action=edit&amp;section=6\" title=\"Edit section: References\">edit</a><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">]</span></span></h2>\n<div class=\"mw-references-wrap\"><ol class=\"references\">\n<li id=\"cite_note-1\"><span class=\"mw-cite-backlink\"><a href=\"#cite_ref-1\">↑</a></span> <span class=\"reference-text\">See <samp>Data/FarmAnimals.xnb</samp> in the game files, specifically <samp>EggItemIds</samp>, which are the valid egg items for each animal type.</span>\n</li>\n</ol></div>\n<h2><span class=\"mw-headline\" id=\"History\">History</span><span class=\"mw-editsection\"><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">[</span><a href=\"/mediawiki/index.php?title=Chicken&amp;action=edit&amp;section=7\" title=\"Edit section: History\">edit</a><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">]</span></span></h2>\n<ul><li><a href=\"/Version_History#1.6\" title=\"Version History\">1.6</a>: Eggs now always give the corresponding color of chicken in the Incubator. Blue chickens can now only be obtained from Marnie's Ranch.</li></ul>\n<table class=\"wikitable\" id=\"navbox\">\n<tbody><tr>\n<th colspan=\"2\"><a href=\"/Animals\" title=\"Animals\">Animals</a> and Produce\n</th></tr>\n<tr>\n<th><a href=\"/Coop\" title=\"Coop\">Coop</a>\n</th>\n<td><a class=\"mw-selflink selflink\">Chicken</a> <sup>(<a href=\"/Egg\" title=\"Egg\">Egg</a> • <a href=\"/Large_Egg\" title=\"Large Egg\">Large Egg</a> • <a href=\"/Egg\" title=\"Egg\">Brown Egg</a> • <a href=\"/Large_Egg\" title=\"Large Egg\">Large Brown Egg</a>)</sup> • <a href=\"/Dinosaur\" title=\"Dinosaur\">Dinosaur</a> <sup>(<a href=\"/Dinosaur_Egg\" title=\"Dinosaur Egg\">Dinosaur Egg</a>)</sup> • <a href=\"/Duck\" title=\"Duck\">Duck</a> <sup>(<a href=\"/Duck_Egg\" title=\"Duck Egg\">Duck Egg</a> • <a href=\"/Duck_Feather\" title=\"Duck Feather\">Duck Feather</a>)</sup> • <a href=\"/Golden_Chicken\" title=\"Golden Chicken\">Golden Chicken</a> <sup>(<a href=\"/Golden_Egg\" title=\"Golden Egg\">Golden Egg</a>)</sup> • <a href=\"/Rabbit\" title=\"Rabbit\">Rabbit</a> <sup>(<a href=\"/Wool\" title=\"Wool\">Wool</a> • <a href=\"/Rabbit%27s_Foot\" title=\"Rabbit&#39;s Foot\">Rabbit's Foot</a>)</sup> • <a href=\"/Void_Chicken\" title=\"Void Chicken\">Void Chicken</a> <sup>(<a href=\"/Void_Egg\" title=\"Void Egg\">Void Egg</a>)</sup>\n</td></tr>\n<tr>\n<th><a href=\"/Barn\" title=\"Barn\">Barn</a>\n</th>\n<td><a href=\"/Cow\" title=\"Cow\">Cow</a> <sup>(<a href=\"/Milk\" title=\"Milk\">Milk</a> • <a href=\"/Large_Milk\" title=\"Large Milk\">Large Milk</a>)</sup> • <a href=\"/Goat\" title=\"Goat\">Goat</a> <sup>(<a href=\"/Goat_Milk\" title=\"Goat Milk\">Goat Milk</a> • <a href=\"/Large_Goat_Milk\" title=\"Large Goat Milk\">Large Goat Milk</a>)</sup> • <a href=\"/Sheep\" title=\"Sheep\">Sheep</a>  <sup>(<a href=\"/Wool\" title=\"Wool\">Wool</a>)</sup> • <a href=\"/Ostrich\" title=\"Ostrich\">Ostrich</a> <sup>(<a href=\"/Ostrich_Egg\" title=\"Ostrich Egg\">Ostrich Egg</a>)</sup> • <a href=\"/Pig\" title=\"Pig\">Pig</a> <sup>(<a href=\"/Truffle\" title=\"Truffle\">Truffle</a>)</sup>\n</td></tr>\n<tr>\n<th><a href=\"/Fish_Pond\" title=\"Fish Pond\">Fish Pond</a>\n</th>\n<td><a href=\"/Fish\" title=\"Fish\">Fish</a> <sup>(<a href=\"/Roe\" title=\"Roe\">Roe</a>)</sup>\n</td></tr>\n<tr>\n<th class=\"no-wrap\"><a href=\"/Slime_Hutch\" title=\"Slime Hutch\">Slime Hutch</a>\n</th>\n<td><a href=\"/Slimes\" title=\"Slimes\">Slimes</a> <sup>(<a href=\"/Slime\" title=\"Slime\">Slime</a> • <a href=\"/Slime_Ball\" title=\"Slime Ball\">Slime Ball</a> • <a href=\"/Slime_Egg\" title=\"Slime Egg\">Slime Egg</a>)</sup>\n</td></tr>\n<tr>\n<th>Other\n</th>\n<td><a href=\"/Animals#Cat_or_Dog\" title=\"Animals\">Cat</a> • <a href=\"/Animals#Cat_or_Dog\" title=\"Animals\">Dog</a> • <a href=\"/Animals#Horse\" title=\"Animals\">Horse</a> • <a href=\"/Animals#Additional_Pets\" title=\"Animals\">Turtle</a>\n</td></tr>\n</tbody></table>\n<!-- \nNewPP limit report\nCached time: 20260414021650\nCache expiry: 86400\nDynamic content: false\nComplications: []\nCPU time usage: 0.147 seconds\nReal time usage: 0.162 seconds\nPreprocessor visited node count: 4068/1000000\nPost‐expand include size: 17747/2097152 bytes\nTemplate argument size: 2114/2097152 bytes\nHighest expansion depth: 10/40\nExpensive parser function count: 0/100\nUnstrip recursion depth: 0/20\nUnstrip post‐expand size: 6868/5000000 bytes\nLua time usage: 0.008/7.000 seconds\nLua memory usage: 740 KB/50 MB\n-->\n<!--\nTransclusion expansion time report (%,ms,calls,template)\n100.00%  115.689      1 -total\n 40.28%   46.599      1 Template:Infobox_animal\n 33.30%   38.522      2 Template:Qualityprice\n 30.18%   34.918      5 Template:Description\n 14.62%   16.912      5 Template:Name\n  9.57%   11.077      8 Template:Overlayimg\n  4.88%    5.650      2 Template:Duration\n  3.60%    4.160      7 Template:Price\n  2.78%    3.218      1 Template:History\n  1.66%    1.922      1 Template:InfoboxSEO\n-->\n\n<!-- Saved in parser cache with key enwiki:pcache:idhash:1890-0!canonical and timestamp 20260414021650 and revision id 189239\n -->\n</div>",
      "wikitext": "{{Infobox animal\n|image    = White Chicken.png\n|image2   = Brown Chicken.png\n|image3   = Blue Chicken.png\n|buyprice = 800\n|building = {{Name|Coop}}\n|produce  = {{Name|Egg}}{{Name|Brown Egg}}{{Name|Large Egg}}{{Name|Large Brown Egg}}\n}} \n:''See also: [[Golden Chicken]], [[Void Chicken]]''\nThe '''Chicken''' is a farm [[Animals|animal]] that lives in a [[Coop]]. Chickens can be purchased at [[Marnie's Ranch]] for {{Price|800}} or hatched by placing an [[Egg]] into an [[Incubator]], taking {{duration|9,000m (5d 16h 40m)|class=inline}} to incubate, or {{duration|4,500m (2d 21h 40m)|class=inline}} with the [[Farming#Farming Skill|Coopmaster Profession]]. Additionally, two chickens are present on the farm by default on the Meadowlands [[Farm Maps|Farm Map]].\n\n==Color==\nChickens are colored White, Brown, or Blue. The Blue variety can be obtained only after seeing [[Shane]]'s 8-heart event. The color of the chicken is assigned randomly by the game when a chicken is purchased.\n\nWhile selecting a coop for a Chicken purchased from Marnie's Ranch, a message is shown stating \"Choose a Coop for your new White/Brown/Blue Chicken\". Cancelling the purchase returns the player to the purchase window, where they can try again for the desired color.\n\nAn [[Incubator]] will hatch a brown chicken from a [[Egg|Brown Egg]] and a white chicken from a regular Egg (or the corresponding Large variants). This means blue chickens cannot be obtained using an Incubator.<ref>See <samp>Data/FarmAnimals.xnb</samp> in the game files, specifically <samp>EggItemIds</samp>, which are the valid egg items for each animal type.</ref>\n\nWhite and blue chickens produce white eggs, and brown chickens produce brown eggs, so it makes a difference in completing the [[Community Center]] [[Bundles]], especially if [[Options#Advanced Options|Remixed Bundles]] is not chosen at start of game.\n\n==Produce==\n{{main article|Animals#Produce}}\nChickens who eat every day mature after 3 nights have passed. A mature and fed chicken produces a white or brown [[Egg]] every day, which can be placed in an [[Incubator]] to hatch another chicken, or sold for {{Price|50}}. Once sufficient [[Animals#Friendship|friendship]] and happiness is reached, it has a chance to produce a [[Large Egg]] or [[Large Egg|Large Brown Egg]] which sells for {{Price|95}}.\n\nAn Egg can be placed in the [[Mayonnaise Machine]] to produce [[Mayonnaise]], which sells for {{Price|190}} or {{Price|285}} depending on quality.\n\n{|class=\"wikitable roundedborder\"\n!Image\n!Name\n!Description\n!Sell Price\n|-\n|[[File:Egg.png]] [[File:Brown Egg.png]]\n|[[Egg]]<br />[[Egg|Brown Egg]]\n|{{Description|Egg}}<br />{{Description|Brown Egg}}\n|{{Qualityprice|Egg|50|dsv=false}}\n|-\n|[[File:Large Egg.png]] [[File:Large Brown Egg.png]]\n|[[Large Egg]]<br />[[Large Egg|Large Brown Egg]]\n|{{Description|Large Egg}}<br />{{Description|Large Brown Egg}}\n|{{Qualityprice|Large Egg|95|dsv=false}}\n|}\n\n==Blue Chickens==\n[[File:BlueChick.png|75px|thumb|A blue chick]]After seeing [[Shane]]'s 8-heart event, each chicken you purchase from [[Marnie]] has a 25% chance of being blue. Aside from appearance, blue chickens are identical to regular white and brown chickens. One subtle benefit to this alternative color is that blue chickens are much easier to spot in a field of grass.\n\nBlue chickens are hatched as blue chicks.\n\n==Selling==\nIt is possible to sell Chickens. The amount of [[gold]] obtained for doing so is dependent on how many hearts the animal has. The more hearts; the higher amount of gold fetched for selling it. The amount of gold obtained for selling a maximum-heart Chicken is {{Price|1040}}.\n\nTo sell a coop or barn animal, right-click the animal after petting. The friendship/mood interface appears. Move the cursor over the gold coin button at the right to see how much you can sell the animal for. Click that button and the confirmation that follows to complete the sale.\n\n==Trivia==\n*A blue chicken egg was added to the game [[wikipedia:Terraria|Terraria]] with ConcernedApe's permission in October 2022.\n\n==References==\n<references/>\n\n==History==\n{{History|1.6|Eggs now always give the corresponding color of chicken in the Incubator. Blue chickens can now only be obtained from Marnie's Ranch.}}\n\n{{NavboxAnimals}}\n\n[[Category:Coop animals]]\n\n[[de:Huhn]]\n[[es:Gallina]]\n[[fr:Poule]]\n[[it:Gallina]]\n[[ja:ニワトリ]]\n[[ko:닭]]\n[[hu:Csirke]]\n[[pt:Galinha]]\n[[ru:Курица]]\n[[tr:Tavuk]]\n[[zh:鸡]]"
